{"tid":2410705,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彈劾無罪後 再有民主黨議員控告川普密謀煽動國會暴動「違反3K黨法案」","createTime":"2021-02-16T23:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T02:41:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2386c0e91935822cce82e1bf609a79ce4cb8a938","tid":2410705,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T23:09:24.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨籍眾議院國土安全委員會主席湯普森（Bennie Thompson）周二（16日）向華盛頓聯邦地區法院提出控告前總統川普、他的律師朱利安尼及兩個右翼團體，指出他們密謀煽動了1月6日的國會暴動，而這違反了早在19世紀就制定的「3K黨法案」。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n早在1871年就簽署生效的「3K黨法案」，是當時美國在經歷內戰後，政府為了防止白人至上主義組織再度崛起，同時保護非裔民眾所制定，而法案內還有一項鮮少被提及的條款：禁止任何民眾藉陰謀論阻礙聯邦官員工作。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210217/W35VQOLS7BA3LNPIU3WAKQCIGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210217%2FW35VQOLS7BA3LNPIU3WAKQCIGM%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BYyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=24a34a97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210217%2FW35VQOLS7BA3LNPIU3WAKQCIGM%2F&h=881c74e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210217/W35VQOLS7BA3LNPIU3WAKQCIGM/</a>"},{"pid":"bfdb1134944817b982435c7a544d936e6b598eb7","tid":2410705,"uid":364767,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T23:13:44.000Z","msg":"煽動美國暴亂的是間諜，好多論壇媒體已被入侵<br />\n這些間諜在網上號召市民四圍搞事"},{"pid":"fdb0aa2336dd0fe100df104b74e91f73f9a6029b","tid":2410705,"uid":37232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T23:20:14.000Z","msg":"3K黨法係共和黨立法，用黎對付當時親民主黨的3k黨<br />\n<br />\nps. 當時共和黨支持平權廢除種族隔離，而民主黨支持種族隔離"},{"pid":"21839517252e7dc07726a5db8b50e588eacf9f22","tid":2410705,"uid":183758,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T23:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">民主匪黨</span>"},{"pid":"5dffb4c2538544a4c18d584ab9e87c6fa2f559d9","tid":2410705,"uid":297453,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"